The George Brown College offers an Online Health Information Management (C139) program. The program content, career options, and student experiences can be learned by watching a previously recorded information session. Interested individuals can contact Kimberly Durofil, the Program Coordinator, at kdurofil@georgebrown.ca.

Application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more can be kept up-to-date by signing up. The College's phone number is 416-415-2000, and the TTY number is 1-877-515-5559. For inquiries, email ask.george@georgebrown.ca.

The information on the website may be subject to change without notice and should not be viewed as a representation, offer, or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
